{"tid":1551002,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇師傅識整蛋包飯","createTime":"2019-09-07T19:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T23:05:17.000Z","uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"831924d7b2aec460ae0cd1e5db8967dd94a247f0","tid":1551002,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:55:57.000Z","msg":"之前整過兩次都推到散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYouTube 睇過好多教學片<br />\n但好多都係遠鏡<br />\n睇唔到重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日諗住買兩排雞蛋試整<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9ba9ab4033d44aa61ee401d0f0bca18b6e4fb2","tid":1551002,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:56:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e31a0ea70e9222812f5a112b16ace092a6082a08","tid":1551002,"uid":193738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:00:55.000Z","msg":"鑊既問題"},{"pid":"1134a9e5370feb503aef777c8b18a32cee34692d","tid":1551002,"uid":193738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:02:21.000Z","msg":"可以試下落多